rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0001
rows.name:
Meleph-sama!
We have been expecting you.

rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0002
rows.name:
You have heard my business here,
I presume? We require passage to
the Cliffs of Mors.

rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0003
rows.name:
Yes, ma'am!
The preparations are all complete.

rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0004
rows.name:
I doubt this will be an easy voyage...
Are you sure you're up to it?

rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0006
rows.name:
By order of His Majesty the Emperor,
only the finest of sailors have been
gathered for this assignment!

rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0007
rows.name: I'll have to thank him for that later...
